== 製作 ==
=== 開發 ===
{{Multiple image|align=right|image1=Michelle Pfeiffer and David E. Kelley.jpg|width1=130|image2=Jean-Marc Vallée, Genie Awards 2012.jpg|width2=120|image3=Andrea Arnold (Cannes Film Festival 2012).jpg|width3=107|footer=[[黃金時段艾美獎|黃金時段艾美獎]]得主[[大衛·E·凱利|大衛·E·凱利]]（左圖左）執筆，[[讓-馬克·瓦雷|尚-馬克·瓦利]]（中）與[[安德莉亞·阿諾德|安德莉亞·阿諾德]]（右）分別執導1、2季。}}
2015年5月8日，[[HBO|HBO]]宣布直接預訂一系列由兩位[[奧斯卡金像獎|奧斯卡]][[奧斯卡最佳女主角獎|影-{后}-]][[妮可·基嫚|妮可·基嫚]]與[[麗絲·韋花絲潘|瑞絲·薇斯朋]]主演、[[黃金時段艾美獎|黃金時段艾美獎]]得主[[大衛·E·凱利|大衛·E·凱利]]撰寫、改編自[[澳大利亞|澳洲]]作家{{link-en|黎安·莫瑞亞蒂|Liane Moriarty}}的暢銷{{link-en|小謊言 (小說)|Big Little Lies (novel)|同名小說}}的有限劇集<ref name="order">{{cite news|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|title='Big Little Lies' Limited Series Starring Nicole Kidman & Reese Witherspoon Picked Up By HBO|url=http://deadline.com/2015/05/big-little-lies-nicole-kidman-reese-witherspoon-hbo-limited-series-1201423026/|accessdate=2015-05-08|work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline Hollywood]]|date=2015-05-08|archive-date=2018-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180617092932/https://deadline.com/2015/05/big-little-lies-nicole-kidman-reese-witherspoon-hbo-limited-series-1201423026/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。薇斯朋與其太平洋標準製作公司夥伴{{link-en|布魯娜·帕潘卓亞|Bruna Papandrea}}和基嫚的[[花開影業|花開影業]]夥伴波·薩里（{{lang|en|Per Saari}}）等四人及凱利將共同擔任執行製作，而原作家莫瑞亞蒂則將擔任製作一職<ref name="order"/>。10月23日，[[讓-馬克·瓦雷|尚-馬克·瓦利]]正商討執導本劇第一集，並將為他的電視劇處女作，而其製作夥伴{{link-en|奈森·羅斯|Nathan Ross}}則確定將擔任本劇製作<ref>{{cite news|url=http://deadline.com/2015/10/jean-marc-vallee-big-little-lies-hbo-nicole-kidman-reese-witherspoon-david-e-kelley-1201592401/|title=Jean-Marc Vallee In Talks To Helm HBO's 'Big Little Lies' With Nicole Kidman, Reese Witherspoon|accessdate=2017-02-22|work=Deadline Hollywood|author=Mike Fleming Jr|date=2015-10-23|archive-date=2020-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201205155706/https://deadline.com/2015/10/jean-marc-vallee-big-little-lies-hbo-nicole-kidman-reese-witherspoon-david-e-kelley-1201592401/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。12月17日，HBO證實瓦利將執導本劇全季7集集數，同時將與其夥伴羅斯共同身兼執行製作<ref>{{cite news|last=Petski|first=Denise|title=Jean-Marc Vallée To Direct All 7 Episodes Of HBO's 'Big Little Lies'|url=http://deadline.com/2015/12/jean-marc-vallee-direct-all-episodes-hbo-big-little-lies-1201668906/|accessdate=2016-01-10|work=Deadline Hollywood|date=2015-12-17|archive-date=2017-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170622000858/http://deadline.com/2015/12/jean-marc-vallee-direct-all-episodes-hbo-big-little-lies-1201668906/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

本劇於2016年1月底正式在[[加利福尼亞州|加利福尼亞州]][[蒙特雷_(加利福尼亞州)|蒙特里]]開拍<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.onlocationvacations.com/2016/01/25/64259/|title='Big Little Lies', starring Nicole Kidman and Reese Witherspoon, is filming in Monterey, CA this week|publisher=On Location Movies|accessdate=2016-01-26|archive-date=2016-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160126084721/http://www.onlocationvacations.com/2016/01/25/64259/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。10月，HBO釋出首波預告片<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/tv-and-radio/video/2016/oct/18/first-look-at-nicole-kidman-in-hbos-big-little-lies-video?CMP=soc_568|title=First look at Nicole Kidman in HBO's Big Little Lies – video|publisher=[[衛報|衛報]]|accessdate=2016-10-18|archive-date=2020-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200813172029/https://www.theguardian.com/tv-and-radio/video/2016/oct/18/first-look-at-nicole-kidman-in-hbos-big-little-lies-video?CMP=soc_568|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

雖然劇集最初以有限劇集的類型推出，但在本劇首播獲得好評後，劇組有意製作第2季<ref>{{cite news|url=http://deadline.com/2017/09/big-little-lies-season-2-reese-witherspoon-nicole-kidman-liane-moriarty-emmys-backstage-1202172085/|title='Big Little Lies' Season 2: “I'm Thinking About It,” Says Producer-Author Liane Moriarty|work=Deadline Hollywood|author=Anthony D'Alessandro|date=2017-09-17|accessdate=2017-12-08|archive-date=2021-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211203750/https://deadline.com/2017/09/big-little-lies-season-2-reese-witherspoon-nicole-kidman-liane-moriarty-emmys-backstage-1202172085/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://deadline.com/2017/09/big-little-lies-season-2-renewal-the-night-of-veep-final-season-1202172280/|title=Emmy Winner 'Big Little Lies' Closer To Season 2, HBO Boss “Hopeful” For More 'The Night Of', Teases “Great” 'Veep' Finale|work=Deadline Hollywood|author=Nellie Andreeva|date=2017-09-18|accessdate=2017-12-08|archive-date=2021-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211182640/https://deadline.com/2017/09/big-little-lies-season-2-renewal-the-night-of-veep-final-season-1202172280/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並在2017年12月8日，由HBO正式宣布續訂第2季7集集數<ref name="Season 2">{{cite news|url=http://deadline.com/2017/12/big-little-lies-season-2-greenlighted-hbo-nicole-kidman-reese-witherspoon-return-andrea-arnold-direct-1202222921/|title='Big Little Lies' Followup Is A Go At HBO With Nicole Kidman & Reese Witherspoon Back; Andrea Arnold Tapped To Direct|work=Deadline Hollywood|author=Nellie Andreeva|date=2017-12-08|accessdate=2017-12-08|archive-date=2017-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171209044222/http://deadline.com/2017/12/big-little-lies-season-2-greenlighted-hbo-nicole-kidman-reese-witherspoon-return-andrea-arnold-direct-1202222921/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。執導第1季並奪得艾美獎的瓦利因行程衝突而退出第2季導演一職<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tvline.com/2017/11/09/big-little-lies-season-2-cast-jean-marc-vallee-leaving/|title=''Big Little Lies'': Who's Not Returning?|publisher={{link-en|TVLine|TVLine}}|author=Michael Ausiello|date=2017-11-09|accessdate=2017-12-08|archive-date=2021-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211235727/https://tvline.com/2017/11/09/big-little-lies-season-2-cast-jean-marc-vallee-leaving/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但他將繼續留任執行製作，並由電影《{{link-en|2016美國甜心|American Honey (film)}}》導演[[安德莉亞·阿諾德|安德莉亞·阿諾德]]執導第2季全季7集集數<ref name="Season 2"/>。

