== 宣傳與發行 ==
=== 市場營銷 ===
2016年10月16日，HBO釋出了劇集的先行預告短片<ref>{{cite web |last1=Lincoln |first1=Ross A. |title='Big Little Lies' Teaser: Someone's Papa Was A Rollin' Stone |url=http://deadline.com/2016/10/hbo-big-little-lies-first-teaser-1201837276/ |website=Deadline |accessdate=2018-03-15 |date=2016-10-16 |language=en-US |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108103759/https://deadline.com/2016/10/hbo-big-little-lies-first-teaser-1201837276/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。12月5日，HBO播放了劇集的正式預告片<ref>{{cite web |last1=Evans |first1=Greg |title='Big Little Lies' Trailer: Watch HBO's Murderous Moms Of Monterey |url=http://deadline.com/2016/12/big-little-lies-trailer-hbo-reese-witherspoon-nicole-kidman-1201864974/ |website=Deadline |accessdate=2018-03-15 |date=2016-12-06 |language=en-US |archive-date=2021-02-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211170941/https://deadline.com/2016/12/big-little-lies-trailer-hbo-reese-witherspoon-nicole-kidman-1201864974/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2019年4月14日，在《[[冰與火之歌：權力遊戲|冰與火之歌：權力遊戲]]》[[权力的游戏_(第八季)|第八季]]首播前，HBO釋出了《美麗心計》第二季的先行預告短片，并宣佈第二季將於2019年6月9日首播<ref>{{cite web |last1=Nyren |first1=Erin |title='Big Little Lies' Season 2 Teaser Drops, Premiere Date Announced |url=https://variety.com/2019/tv/news/big-little-lies-season-2-teaser-trailer-premiere-date-1203189279/ |website=variety |accessdate=2019-05-15 |date=2019-04-14 |language=en-US |archive-date=2020-08-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200812015909/https://variety.com/2019/tv/news/big-little-lies-season-2-teaser-trailer-premiere-date-1203189279/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

