2017年2月7日，HBO在[[加利福尼亞州|加利福尼亞州]][[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]的[[中國戲院|中國戲院]]舉行了劇集首映典禮<ref>{{cite web |last1=Jensen |first1=Erin |title=Reese Witherspoon, daughter Ava Phillippe are twins at 'Big Little Lies' premiere |url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/entertainthis/2017/02/08/big-little-lies-premiere-reese-witherspoon-ava-phillippe-kathreen-khavari/97637918/ |website=USA Today |accessdate=2018-03-16 |language=en |date=2017-02-08 |archive-date=2018-02-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180222165247/https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/entertainthis/2017/02/08/big-little-lies-premiere-reese-witherspoon-ava-phillippe-kathreen-khavari/97637918/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Porreca |first1=Brian |title='Big Little Lies' Premiere: Cast Talks Murder Mystery, TV's Portrayal of Women |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/big-little-lies-premiere-reese-witherspoon-shailene-woodley-nicole-kidman-interviews-97334 |website=The Hollywood Reporter |accessdate=2018-03-16 |language=en |date=2017-02-08 |archive-date=2018-03-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180316152345/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/big-little-lies-premiere-reese-witherspoon-shailene-woodley-nicole-kidman-interviews-97334 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

